# Environment variables for explorenu

# ── Forms ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Formspree endpoint for all lead form submissions (hero form, mini CTAs, scholarship gate).
# 1. Sign up at https://formspree.io (free tier is fine to start)
# 2. Create a new form and copy the endpoint URL
# 3. Paste it below (e.g. https://formspree.io/f/xwkgpqrv)
# 4. Set the same value in your Vercel project dashboard under Environment Variables
#
# TODO (Marketing): replace with the real TargetX/Salesforce webhook URL once available.
# When that endpoint is live, update composables/useLeadForm.ts and the Formspree
# fetch calls in MiniCta.vue and ScholarshipExplorer.vue to point to it instead.
FORMSPREE_URL=
